meFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131310"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131435","id":"zettel.20260420131435","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420131311","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":14,"offset":1823},"end":{"line":42,"column":39,"offset":1848},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131311"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420131435","id":"zettel.20260420131435","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":3,"offset":1927},"end":{"line":46,"column":42,"offset":1966},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":96,"column":3,"offset":8243},"end":{"line":96,"column":28,"offset":8268},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131435"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","id":"zettel.literature.context-anchoring","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":183,"column":3,"offset":12697},"end":{"line":183,"column":28,"offset":12722},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420131435"}],"anchors":{"gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Gagasan","value":"gagasan","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-ini-penting":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Ini Penting","value":"mengapa-ini-penting","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"apa-maksud-murahnya-restart":{"type":"header","text":"Apa Maksud \"Murahnya Restart\"","value":"apa-maksud-murahnya-restart","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"contoh-biaya-restart":{"type":"header","text":"Contoh Biaya Restart","value":"contoh-biaya-restart","line":32,"column":0,"depth":2},"kenapa-ini-jadi-ukuran-keberhasilan":{"type":"header","text":"Kenapa Ini Jadi Ukuran Keberhasilan","value":"kenapa-ini-jadi-ukuran-keberhasilan","line":43,"column":0,"depth":2},"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain":{"type":"header","text":"Hubungan ke Zettel Lain","value":"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain","line":49,"column":0,"depth":2},"sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber","value":"sumber","line":55,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"keberhasilan-context-anchoring-diukur-dari-murahnya-restart\">Keberhasilan context anchoring diukur dari murahnya restart<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#keberhasilan-context-anchoring-diukur-dari-murahnya-restart\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"gagasan\">Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Itu indikator paling konkret bahwa konteks sudah berada di tempat yang benar.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mengapa-ini-penting\">Mengapa Ini Penting<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-ini-penting\"></a></h2>\n<p>Bukan soal AI jadi pintar, tapi soal biaya memulai ulang yang rendah.</p>\n<h2 id=\"apa-maksud-murahnya-restart\">Apa Maksud \"Murahnya Restart\"<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#apa-maksud-murahnya-restart\"></a></h2>\n<p>Penulis menjadikan pertanyaan ini sebagai tes praktis: apakah saya bisa menutup sesi sekarang dan membuka sesi baru tanpa rasa cemas. Kalau jawabannya tidak, berarti konteks penting masih terjebak di chat.</p>\n<p>Biaya restart di sini bukan cuma teknis. Ini mencakup:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>waktu untuk menjelaskan ulang keputusan sebelumnya,</li>\n<li>risiko AI mengulang alternatif yang sudah ditolak,</li>\n<li>waktu untuk mengembalikan konteks produktif yang hilang,</li>\n<li>potensi membuat saran baru yang bertentangan dengan niat awal.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contoh-biaya-restart\">Contoh Biaya Restart<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#contoh-biaya-restart\"></a></h2>\n<p>Kalau sebuah fitur diskusi multi-sesi tanpa feature document, sesi baru mungkin harus:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>membaca ulang chat panjang atau meraba-raba history,</li>\n<li>menanyakan kembali apakah <code>RetryQueue</code> sudah ditolak,</li>\n<li>mengonfirmasi lagi batasan <code>email-only v1</code>,</li>\n<li>mengulang status implementasi terakhir.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Semua itu bisa memakan waktu puluhan menit sampai jam, bahkan sebelum kerja nyata kembali berjalan.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kenapa-ini-jadi-ukuran-keberhasilan\">Kenapa Ini Jadi Ukuran Keberhasilan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kenapa-ini-jadi-ukuran-keberhasilan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Kalau sesi baru bisa langsung melanjutkan dari dokumentasi fitur yang sudah ada, itu berarti konteks ada di tempat yang bisa diakses ulang. Insiden kehilangan konteks berkurang, dan biaya restart jatuh ke level yang jauh lebih rendah.</p>\n<p>Itu adalah indeks praktis bahwa context anchoring berhasil: bukan karena AI semakin pintar, tapi karena konteks disimpan di luar chat dan siap dipakai ulang.</p>\n<h2 id=\"hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\">Hubungan ke Zettel Lain<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#hubungan-ke-zettel-lain\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mendukung <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — klaim diambil dari Paragraf 38.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131310\">Percakapan AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan</a> — tesis utama bahwa chat AI adalah medium berpikir, bukan tempat penyimpanan keputusan.</li>\n<li>Lihat juga <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420131311\">Kolaborasi manusia multi-hari memindahkan memori kerja ke dokumen bersama</a> — baseline kolaborasi manusia yang transfer konteks ke dokumen.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"sumber\">Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a> — Paragraf 38</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #a03623;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettel\">zettel</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-collaboration (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">context-anchoring (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.context-anchoring\">Context Anchoring — memindahkan konteks keputusan dari chat ke dokumen hidup</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"